  	    "alternativeHeadline": "News flash: The restaurant pastry chef is dead, a casualty of American dining becoming more, well, casual. The silver lining? A bumper crop of incredible bakeries, patisseries, doughnut joints, and specialized dessert temples all over the land. Chef Chang picks his sweetest spots",
